hest trouble, he's - he was seventy I think, something like that. And then there came a - then came the girl. My eldest sister, and then - my other sister. Mabel. And then me. And then Rose, my Rose was the youngest one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 How much younger than you was Rose?
