 a day. My sister had a doll, she hadn't bought me nothing 'cos I'd misbehaved, she told me she wouldn't buy me nothing, she'd been somewhere, and you wont get nothing, you've been too cheeky, until you learn your manners you don't get nothing. So my sist
er got this - little wax doll she used to get that day. But I got hold of this doll and I got the tongs out - and I flattened it right flat. And of course she was crying.
