now. She - she's about - oh I suppose - she wasn't very old, she's younger than me any rate, we got our photo taken somewhere for these kids, anyhow - this bloody doll, and then I went and - and she - mother'd gone out and I got all the black paint and I 
p
ained all the knocker, this day, and the old girl came in and went to pull her gloves, her new gloves onto the knocker to - rat-tat-tat on the door, and oh of course I got another bashing for that. I was always getting a row. I was always getting - good h
idings, but I don't know.
