Oh well, I - when I was a kid I always wanted to grow up to be a nurse. Always wanted to be a nurse, but I never - materialized, there was never enough money I don't think, anyhow if there was - my mother didn't intend to spend it on me anyway.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Do you think your mother and father brought you up to consider certain things important in life?
