l, you managed, you saved, what you wanted to buy you saved - you saved 'til you got it sort of thin and - and - and all them sort of things you know - she's very fair in things - like my brother, he done a paper round I remember once and he pinched too b
o
b, you know, it's only like the - she didn't half whack him. And she wasn't satisfied with that, she went to the stall and the school caned him, and do you know he never sat down, poor little bugger, for a week. But my father was the one that pulled her u
p about it. He said, Amy, he said to her - there's no \{ILLEGIBLE\}
 she said, well he'll never steal anything more. She said, I'll cut your blooming fingers off, she said, and all he pinched was two bob, but he never forget it. Years ago, just before ths star
