all the way down, and - and it was posh area then, I remember the - when - she - when she did - start, we got older, and she started going doing a bit of work she worked for some maiden ladies up in Ivydale Road where used to go and - where she used to do
 
a bit of work sometimes, and we used to go up there and Christmas time, parties, this lady was ever so good, she used to send her - one of them baskets full of - clothes for us all you know. And Christmas tree. Well I've never seen children have anything 
