\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Yes - well Christmas - Christmas Eve and a great big Christmas tree in them gr}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
