\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 No. No, she's pretty - good like that, and it all used to get - 'cos we all ate well, you know, we were pretty -
