\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Well - we always had to go to bed by eight o'clock at night, yes.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 What would happen if you didn't?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Oh - she'd see you was, we was there don't worry, when we were kids.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Who put you to bed?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Oh had to put ourselves to bed, had to make our own beds.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 From very early on?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Yes, all - yes, when we was getting on, went to school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 You said you had two younger sisters and you had
 two older sisters and two brothers as well, did the older ones help the younger ones in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 
Oh - oh yes, yes, they all helped - they helped one another. But - the only one - that they seemed to make a fuss of, my mum and dad, was the youngest o
ne, Rosie. My father, he'd come in from work and ask where she was, and you know she'd be; miles out somewhere you know, playing around, he'd say, go and find her, you go and get her in, and - and don't matter what you was doing you had to leave everythin
g to go and find her, to - so that they could see here, while we were out I don't know where they ever thought she had got to I don't know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Would the younger children help - the older ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Yes. Yes. Pretty good like that, mm. Well you had to, my mum didn't believe in waiting on you all the time. You had to help yourself a bit.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 You said about this lodger, Mrs Emery?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Ermery, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Did she eat with you when you had meals?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 No, no, they lived upstairs, had their own place you see.
 That was when I - when we was at home, my mum used to let the two top rooms, when we lived up in - at Tappersfield Road you see.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 And you say you each had your own room to sleep in?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Oh we had our own rooms to sleep in, boys in one and the girls 
in the other. She used to put the beds for all the girls and the boys in the other. Oh she didn't -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 So there'd be the three bedrooms with the parents and the four}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16659317\charrsid1641457  }{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 the one for the Emery's?
\par 
