\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 You say your sister Rose never quite made it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 No. No. Oh she used to do the - all this - la - singing, yes, oh yes. I used to go and play the piano for her on the - o
n the concert halls and things like that you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11756613 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 What kind of things would she sing, sort of opera?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid6241478 LE  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3736647\charrsid1641457 Opera things and - Danny Boy, she used to sing Danny Boy, that was one of her songs. And all that business, oh dear.
