h
e - I don't know that she ever thought he wasn't capable of doing these things so - I suppose the old chap thought - well he wasn't old but - I suppose he thought well she don't think I'm capable I wouldn't do 'em, so - he never used to do 'em, if she wan
ted anything done - the house, she always used to get on to the landlord to do it you know.
