e and I'd been and got me wages from work and I'd come home and took 'em to me - took 'em in me pocket round to the picture palace and went in for three}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid2642704\charrsid1641457  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
